  <p>
    <code>Reranker</code> is implemented today by:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <a href="/llmrouter/docs/providers/cohere"><strong>Cohere</strong></a>
      &mdash; <code>rerank-v3.5</code>,
      <code>rerank-english-v3.0</code>,
      <code>rerank-multilingual-v3.0</code>.
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="/llmrouter/docs/providers/voyage"><strong>Voyage</strong></a>
      &mdash; <code>rerank-2</code>, <code>rerank-2-lite</code>.
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="/llmrouter/docs/providers/openai-compatible"><strong>Together</strong></a>
      via the OpenAI-compatible provider with
      <code>WithBaseURL("https://api.together.xyz/v1")</code> &mdash;
      <code>Salesforce/Llama-Rank-V1</code>.
    </li>
  </ul>

